Hello. Our Robotics Team here at GKHS High School have a problem. I am getting this error repeatedly and I have no clue on how to fix it. The error itself is: Unresolved dependency: com.revrobotics:CANSparkMax:1.5.1Java(0). The GKHS Software Team is very new to the whole programming thing, and if we could get this fixed, hopefully we can have a moving robot. Thank you.

403210:

SparkMax

It looks like you may not have added your vendordep for this.

From your top menu bar select “View”
Select Command Pallete
Input in Manage Vendor dependencies
input this url in the field that comes up : https://software-metadata.revrobotics.com/REVLib-2025.json hit enter
